{
  "text": "Expression (13) is similar to equation 3.1 of [CITATION_1] , except that the latter relates instead to the full structure function. What differs is the factor in parentheses (the full expression has (1 \u2212 J 0 (Kr)). The two expressions behave similarly however, acting as high pass filters (Fig. 1) . In the limit of small separations, the filter in (13) is:",
